{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"energyConfiguration"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"The energy configuration of the receiver. Lets you enable and customize the energy management.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is copied on setting, so mutating the configuration after setting will not change the behavior.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Instead, re-configure your instance and set it again.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerViewController"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerViewController(py)energyConfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"energyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(